65 Sukhasahagataduka
Sukhasahagataduka
84.
274Nasukhasahagataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
275Nanasukhasahagataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nanasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi.
276Nasukhasahagatañca nanasukhasahagatañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā…  tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
277Hetuyā nava…pe…  purejāte āsevane cha…pe…  avigate nava.
